_comment: Generated by generate_vectors.py. Input bytes, which you can get from generate_input.py, are generated by incrementing a 4-byte little-endian integer, starting with 1. For example, an input of length 10 would be the bytes [1, 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 3, 0]. All of the BLAKE2s hashes are computed with a 16-byte digest length.
